\is1 Introduction
\ip Due daruwa katuyuan of this the \bk First letter of John\bk*: 1.) the pegbagget of readers of pegnengneng concerning the God and of Anak din si Jesus the messiah; and 2.) the warning kandan of it's necessary not eg-ikul of not true/correct teaching egpakadereet just of unity ran there to Master. Migkahi that not true/correct teacher of si Jesus kun Anak of God not egkeyitabu person sikandin iling kanta. Migpanulu again sikandan the kaluwasan, ware kun kalabetan of living righteous/honest/sensible and of loving of duma.
\ip Na, of pegsupak of sika teaching, mig-ayad-ayad migpangguhud si John, si Jesus the messiah true/correct iya person, and very rin again ipasabut the langun migpalintutuu of Jesus and the miggeyinawa of God, it's necessary egpaheyinaweey also the tagse sabeka.
